               <head>Astrolabes and astronomy</head>
               <msContents class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2009116092 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2001000141">
                  <summary>Collection of works on astrolabes and astronomy</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2009116092" n="1" xml:id="Uk_IO_Islamic_3786-item1">
                     <locus from="1" to="33">ff. 1-33</locus>
                     <note>
                        <p>Manual on the use of astrolabes, with details on astronomy and mathematics, organised into 50 bāb, but lacking a preface, title, or the author's name </p>
                        <p>The work may be identical with the <title>Irshād</title> of Nāṣir al-Dīn Ḥaydar ibn Muḥammad Shīrāzī
                        </p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="per">Persian</textLang>
                  </msItem>
